snippet.textDisplay:
First thoughts:

Rock M Sakura: Insane, hilarious
Dahlia Sin: Banjee charismatic beauty, confident
Sherry Pie: Camp, Sweet, Smart, Love how she paints her face. But I read testimonies that describe her as a sexual predator, so now I can't look at her without being disgusted.
Jan: Not really into her style, cringed at her trying to explain her reference, but she has a beautiful voice, and I'm really wondering what her original name was lol.
Jaida Essence Hall: Not really into her look, don't know about her personality yet. We'll see
Aiden Zhane: She brings something different to the cast. Will it be good? We'll see
snippet.textOriginal:

Rock M Sakura: Insane, hilarious
Dahlia Sin: Banjee charismatic beauty, confident

Jan: Not really into her style, cringed at her trying to explain her reference, but she has a beautiful voice, and I'm really wondering what her original name was lol.

Aiden Zhane: She brings something different to the cast. Will it be good? We'll see
